---
title: Rosemary Demi-Glace Steak with Mashed Potatoes & Roasted Veggies
description: These, friends, are not your average pork chops. In fact, our chefs gave ‘em a steak-like treatment, transforming the everyday protein into something above and beyond. The chops are seared to perfection, then drizzled with an ultra-savory, rosemary-flecked pan sauce. The sides? Just as impressive. We’re serving up creamy mashed potatoes and roasted carrots and onion wedges to round everything out. Prepare for a flavor explosion.
